dialogue.name: Wahoooey!!! Best episode of the season! Anime of the year! Best leading role goes to Gummy!
Mom and dad are gonna love this episode!
This is the beginning of a super-tacular, new arc in Gummy's Grand Tales!
That was mega cool! Though why does this still feel like a filler episode..?
Weheheh... Every good protagonist has to start somewhere, right..?
